name: Bitcoin
details: Bitcoin is a decentralized digital currency, without a central bank or single administrator.

name: Ethereum
details: Ethereum is a blockchain platform with its own cryptocurrency, called Ether (ETH) or Ethereum, and its own programming language, called Solidity.

name: Binance Coin
details: Binance Coin (BNB) is a cryptocurrency that can be used to trade and pay fees on the Binance cryptocurrency exchange.

name: Tether USDT
details: Tether opens up decentralized, peer-to-peer networks to a variety of commercial uses.

name: Dash
details: Dash is an open source cryptocurrency. It is an altcoin that was forked from the Bitcoin protocol.

name: Litecoin
details: Litecoin (LTC) is a peer-to-peer cryptocurrency that was set up by Charlie Lee (a former Google employee) in 2011.

name: Telcoin
details: Telcoin is a mobile remittance network built on top of Ethereum. The project plans to compete with existing remittance providers by providing low-cost services directly through mobile carriers.
